name: Protein Dino Brawl Early Prototype
description: Against a caveman who loved his self created muscle bars, but the dinos took them away. For these muscle bars had a unique property to strengthen those who ate it, and feared the caveman getting stronger than them. However, the caveman refuses to let his invention be taken away, and stands up to the dinos. Eating a single muscle bar he had hidden away, he continues on his way to beat em up! And reclaim all his muscle bars.
